headline.main: Curry, Nowitzki Lead Mavericks Past Thunder, 104-89
headline.print_headline: Curry, Nowitzki Lead Mavericks Past Thunder, 104-89

lead_paragraph: It seems so long ago when Dirk Nowitzki was sidelined with a sore Achilles and the Dallas Mavericks were at the bottom of the Western Conference.
